### 2. The Success & PID Lab
**Goal:** Observe how Linux tracks success and process identification.

```bash
# Check Process ID of your current terminal
echo "My Process ID is: $$"

# Check exit status of a successful command
ls /etc/passwd
echo "Success Status (\$?): $?"

# Check exit status of a failing command
ls /fake/folder
echo "Failure Status (\$?): $?"
```

